snippet: The five-story shopping center built earlier this year in a bustling suburb of Accra, Ghana’s capital, collapsed Wednesday.
abstract: Five-story shopping center collapses in suburb of Ghana's capital Accra, killing at least one person and leaving several dozen people trapped in rubble.
lead_paragraph: The five-story shopping center built earlier this year in a bustling suburb of Accra, Ghana’s capital, collapsed Wednesday.

headline.main: Ghana: Shopping Center Collapse Kills One and Traps Dozens in Rubble
headline.print_headline: Ghana: Shopping Center Collapse Kills One and Traps Dozens in Rubble
